title: 6 AM Hour - If I Could Change Something In My Book It Would Be...
description:
Happy Tuesday! Dave is still in Boston (He's back Thursday!) Falen is gearing up for her Spain Trip that she leaves for tomorrow & don't forget it's Prince's Birthday!

Jenny's First Song of the Day: Livin La Vida Loca - Ricky Martin, Dave wants to change some chapters in his book, & More!
